high_descs: Turn around and go straight to the table on the right near the fridge.
Pick up the cup from the table.
Turn around and go straight along the counter to the microwave on the far end of the room.
Place the cup inside the microwave.
Turn around and go to the second table on the opposite end of the room, the one farther away from the fridge.
Pick up the cup from this table.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place two cups in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the coffee table.
Pick up cup from the coffee table.
Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the microwave on your right.
Place cup on the coffee table.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the coffee table.
Pick up cup from the coffee table.
Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the microwave on your right.
Place cup on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Collecting cup from different places and arranging them on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn back and walk straight to reach the coffee table  on the right side
Take a cup from the top of the coffee table
Turn back and walk straight to reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the cup inside the oven and close it.
Turn back and walk towards the coffee table
Take a cup from the top of the coffee table
Turn back and walk straight to reach the microwave oven again
Open the oven and put the cup along with the first cup in the oven and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup in the microwave oven
